snippet.title: The Search for the Dahu - Walkthrough
snippet.description:
The Search for the Dahu walkthrough by Carmel Games - Play at
http://www.mousecity.com/games/point-and-click/the-search-for-the-dahu/

0:36 - Get fishing rod
0:43 - get axe
0:55 - see cabinet combination
1:08 - get metal detector
1:18 - use metal detector, get keys
1:26 - use key, get money and screwdriver
1:39 - use screwdriver, get sign
1:48 - use fishing rod, get pocket knife
2:06 - use axe
2:15 - use pocket knife, get whistle
2:54 - activate generator
3:00 - use sign
3:08 - get hook
3:15 - use hook
3:22- get binoculars 
3:45 - use whistle
3:50 - use binoculars
